{"tid":2304604,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"成日望手機，有無辦法可以戒。","createTime":"2020-11-29T03:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T04:58:53.000Z","uid":148996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ce32fe4a87c030e332fb080e6e3766ef595991d3","tid":2304604,"uid":148996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"我一日到黑都機不離手<br />\n<br />\n雖然視力無太大影響<br />\n<br />\n但都影響身體其他野<br />\n<br />\n例如長期用會影響身體結構（駝背，頸痛）<br />\n<br />\n神經緊張，影響睡眠等等<br />\n<br />\n真係好想戒，個心癮好大<br />\n<br />\n有無咩方法可以推薦下。"},{"pid":"b071d3485089c015095736ef2afe2bf826a7ee9b","tid":2304604,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:27:48.000Z","msg":"震撼教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇其他方法"},{"pid":"5ac97cd56c3ccda900f1d5334eca492e61c34b96","tid":2304604,"uid":12527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:31:25.000Z","msg":"試吓返工收工搭車嘅時候塞入袋𥚃面，而且連歌都唔好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8ffeb778ab7275e1f1d241320f9c63abca4a92","tid":2304604,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"有個app可以set時間唔玩手機<br />\n<br />\n達到某個目標時間會有d獎勵<br />\n(遊戲入面既裝飾品）<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔記得左個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325e180dbdec5e1db7089c19d8b7a4b9cc57f2cb","tid":2304604,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:50:35.000Z","msg":"我買咗個定時鎖 想唔用手機就放入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8b060d55698dff9e7e0e497209dee3a53a7bba","tid":2304604,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"買部Feature Phone"},{"pid":"2502397ce5ca7e566083810299f061cdfaedc757","tid":2304604,"uid":269776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db8ffeb778ab7275e1f1d24132